   268	# r130: btrfs root preserved from r116, now with a dedicated rescue partition.
   269	# Layout (3 primary partitions on the OPERATOR-CHOSEN disk):
   270	#   p1: 1 GB  fat32 ESP    (method{ efi })                     -> /boot/efi
   271	#   p2: 4 GB  ext4  rescue (label NCZRESCUE, NO mountpoint)    -> 72-rescue-partition.sh
