    15	- **Firmware**: REQUIRES `/lib/firmware/arm/mali/arch12.8/mali_csffw.bin` (panthor probes arch-versioned path). Staged at `assets/sky1-firmware/arm/mali/arch12.8/`. -> `renderD128` live.
