    17	- **GPU compute stack (shipped)**: from-source **Mesa 26.1.3** under `/opt/mesa-26.1.3`, redirected as the system Vulkan (panvk) + OpenCL (rusticl) provider (`post-install/16-mesa-gpu-2613.sh`). Stock 26.0.3 panvk couldn't run GPU compute (`VK_ERROR_OUT_OF_DEVICE_MEMORY`, 16-entry buffer cap) and shipped no GPU OpenCL. 26.1.3: A/B-validated +20.6% prefill / +12.9% decode (llama.cpp Vulkan), rusticl FP16 ~3.6 TFLOPS.
